sentences: Kathi Lynn Wilcox (born November 19, 1969) is an American musician.
Wilcox provided bass, guitar, drums, and vocals for the band, which lasted throughout the '90s and is considered one of the definitive bands of the riot grrrl movement.
Wilcox married musician Guy Picciotto from Fugazi, and as of September 2020 the two were living in Brooklyn with their 14 year-old.
